OL,3,CWomen sought after fake banknotes used
OL,4,Cto buy #430 mobile phone
OL,6,FHampshire Police want to trace two
OL,7,Fwomen after fake bank notes were used
OL,8,Fto buy a mobile phone.
OL,10,FIt's reported that the pair arrived at
OL,11,Fa house on May the 12th to collect a
OL,12,Fphone that had been advertised for
OL,13,Fsale on-line.
OL,15,FThey paid #430 in cash and left the
OL,16,Fhouse, but it was then established
OL,17,Fthat the banknotes used were
OL,18,Fcounterfeit.
OL,20,FThe online profile used by the buyers
OL,21,Fwas then deleted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
