OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780301370
OL,3,CWomen sought after fake banknotes used
OL,4,Cto buy #430 mobile phone
OL,6,FOfficers are linking the incident with
OL,7,Ftwo others in the area where mobile
OL,8,Fphones, which were advertised for sale
OL,9,Fonline, were paid for with counterfeit
OL,10,Fcash; Bursledon on April 25 and
OL,11,FFareham on April 26.
OL,13,FOn each occasion hundreds of pounds of
OL,14,Fcounterfeit cash was given in exchange
OL,15,Ffor the phones.
OL,17,FThey are asking anyone who recognises
OL,18,Fthe women to get in touch
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/2
